packages/

## Ignore logs
*.log

## Ignore compiled DLLs and EXEs
*.dll
*.exe

## Ignore .NET Core CLI global tools
.tools/

## Ignore EF Core migrations snapshot (optional)
**/Migrations/*Snapshot.cs
